        <span class="attribution__caption">Note: This tool assumes the borrower paid on time every month that a payment was made and does not account for late fees. The standard monthly payment and final payment calculations are based on a simple interest formula that is common in most used car loans but may not reflect the terms of every loan. Borrowers should use this tool as an estimate. The standard monthly payment may have slight discrepancies depending on how lenders calculate the number of days per month.</span>
    
